{
  "name": "RPlog_Beach_Getaway",
  "title": "A Camp-Out in the Sea Caves",
  "summary": "With Imperial forces seizing Caspar and disposing of Rebel sympathizers, the Jedi pilot Leo Corak flees across the planet carrying a young girl, Gabi, the daughter of the Republic officer Ambrosia. Exhausted, they shelter in a sea cave, where Leo coaxes the frightened child into treating their flight as a camping trip and gently draws out the contents of her pack. Among her toys and keepsakes Gabi produces a data chit her mother prepared, which proves to contain banking codes, funds, and a heartfelt letter entrusting Gabi's care, schooling, and the family's Corellian beach home to Leo. Leo bonds with the girl over a shared love of starfighters before tucking her under his cloak to sleep, then settles at the cave mouth to meditate in the Force as Gabi quietly cries herself toward rest.",
